  "agreementV2Section1Body": "These terms apply to your download, installation, and use of OpenReading and its included features. By selecting “Agree and continue,” you confirm that you have read, understood, and accepted them. If you do not agree, stop using and exit the app. A guardian must consent where required by local law.",
  "@agreementV2Section1Body": {
